%global module cornice
%global desc Helpers to build & document Web Services with Pyramid.

Name:             python-cornice
Version:          5.1.0
Release:          1%{?dist}
BuildArch:        noarch

License:          MPLv2.0
Summary:          Define Web Services in Pyramid
URL:              https://pypi.python.org/pypi/cornice
